item.title: [+1583] McCain Refused To Give 30 Seconds During Iraq War Debate
item.description: Yesterday, Sen. Al Franken (D-MN), acting on the orders of the Senate leadership, refused to grant Sen. Joe Lieberman (I-CT) “an additional moment” to continue speaking on the Senate floor after his 10 minutes expired. McCain got a little cantankerous over the matter and now it looks like someone's a hypocrite...
